However, an additional legally binding Hungarian statement restricts the use of these research results by the Mercedes-Benz Group and its subsidiaries.
No usage rights, access rights, or licensing permissions are granted to the Mercedes-Benz Group at this time.
Any future cooperation is conditional upon a peaceful and unambiguous written agreement between the parties.
Third parties are also requested not to offer solutions based on these results to the Mercedes-Benz Group until these conditions are met.
In case of any legal or interpretative conflict, the original Hungarian text shall prevail.
